---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Privacy Policy"
  description="How Australian Home Collective handles reader contact details and basic website information."
>
  <header class="page-intro">
    <div class="narrow">
      <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="lead">
        This policy explains the kinds of information Australian Home Collective may collect
        and how it may be used.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="content narrow">
    <h2>Information you provide</h2>
    <p>
      If you use the contact form, we may receive your name, email address and the information
      included in your message. We use this to respond, review feedback or assess corrections,
      guide suggestions or relevant website enquiries.
    </p>
    <h2>Website information</h2>
    <p>
      Standard website hosting or analytics tools may collect technical information such as
      browser type, device information, pages visited and approximate location. This helps us
      understand site performance and improve content.
    </p>
    <h2>Affiliate links</h2>
    <p>
      Affiliate partners may use tracking links or cookies to attribute referrals. Their privacy
      practices are governed by their own policies. You should check the relevant retailer or
      partner policy if you want more detail about how they handle information.
    </p>
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy questions, use the <a href="/contact/">Contact page</a>.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
